<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VibeGram</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/Quicksand_Complete/Fonts/WEB/css/quicksand.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/04bf1872c5.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/gsap@3.9.0/dist/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0%;
            padding: 0%;
            text-decoration: none;
            list-style-type: none;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Quicksand-Light';
        }

        :root {
            --darkBlue: #1D203E;
            --darkGrey: #2C2F48;
            --gradientBlue: #314BD5;
            --gradientCyan: #27DCE5;
            --lighPink: #C743AF;
        }

        main {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        :root {
            --darkBlue: #1D203E;
            --darkGrey: #2C2F48;
            --gradientBlue: #314BD5;
            --gradientCyan: #27DCE5;
            --lighPink: #C743AF;
            --myWhite: #ffffff;
        }

        .mainContainer {
            position: relative;
            width: 99%;
            height: 98%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 2;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .mainContainer::before {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            content: "";
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -2;
            border-top-left-radius: 25px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 25px;
            background: linear-gradient(130deg, var(--lighPink), var(--gradientBlue));
            clip-path: polygon(50% 0, 0 0, 0 100%, 100% 100%);
        }

        .mainContainer section {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-content: space-around;
            padding: 0px 10px;

        }

        .mainContainer section::before {
            position: absolute;
            content: "";
            top: 0%;
            left: 0%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            z-index: -2;
            border-radius: 25px;
        }

        .mainContainer section h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: var(--myWhite);

        }

        .mainContainer section .slogan {
            line-height: 75px;
        }

        .mainContainer section .slogan h2 {
            font-size: 65px;
            color: var(--myWhite);

        }

        .mainContainer section .description {
            position: relative;
        }

        .mainContainer section .description p {
            line-height: 30px;
            color: var(--myWhite);
            margin: 2px 0px;
            font-weight: 600;

        }

        .mainContainer section .ratings {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;

        }

        .mainContainer section .install {
            display: flex;

        }

        .mainContainer aside {
            position: relative;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 2;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .btn {
            border: 1px solid var(--gradientBlue);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background-color: var(--gradientBlue);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0px 10px;
            transition: all .4s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: white;
            color: #314BD5;
            border: 1px solid var(--gradientBlue);

        }

        .join {
            position: absolute;
            top: 5%;
            right: 5%;
            z-index: 2;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>
    <main>
        <div class="mainContainer">
            <img src="/assets/tweet.png"
                style="width: 25%; height: auto; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; z-index: -2;">
            <img src="/assets/laptop.png"
                style="width: 25%; height: auto; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 35%; z-index: -2;">
            <section>
                <div class="header"
                    style="width: 100%;display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
                    <h1>VibeGram</h1>
                    <div class="btnJoin">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="slogan">
                    <h2>Connecting Vibes,<h2>
                            <h2>One Message at a Time,</h2>
                            <h2>VibeGram Unleashed.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="description">
                    <p>Where every message becomes a melodic note, weaving harmonious conversations.</p>
                    <p>Immerse yourself in a symphony of connections, transcending words into a rhythmic dialogue.</p>
                    <p>Experience the cadence of communication, where each interaction resonates with the pulse of</p>
                    <p>genuine connections. Join VibeGram and turn every chat into a harmonious experience.</p>

                </div>

                <div class="install">
                    <button class="btn">Download for Windows<i class="fa-brands fa-windows"
                            style="font-size: 25px; margin-left: 8px;"></i></button>
                    <button class="btn">Download for Ios<i class="fa-brands fa-apple"
                            style="font-size: 25px; margin-left: 8px;"></i></button>
                </div>
            </section>
            <aside>
                <button class="btn join" id="joinBtn">Join the VibeGram</button>
                <img src="/assets/phoneScreen.png" style="width: 100%; height: auto;">
            </aside>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script>
        // GSAP animations
        gsap.to(".header", { duration: 2, opacity: 1, y: 0, ease: "power2.out" });
        gsap.to(".slogan h2", { duration: 2, opacity: 1, y: 0, stagger: 0.3, ease: "power2.out" });
        gsap.to(".description p", { duration: 2, opacity: 1, y: 0, stagger: 0.2, ease: "power2.out" });
        gsap.to(".install button", { duration: 2, opacity: 1, y: 0, stagger: 0.3, ease: "power2.out" });
        gsap.to(".join", { duration: 1, opacity: 2, x: 0, ease: "power2.out" });
        gsap.from(".mainContainer img", { duration: 2, opacity: 0, scale: 0.5, ease: "power2.out", stagger: 0.5 });

        // Add more animations as needed
        gsap.from("main", { duration: 1.5, opacity: 0, scale: 0.8, ease: "power2.out" });
        gsap.from("aside", { duration: 1.5, opacity: 0, x: 20, ease: "power2.out" });
        // Trigger animations on scroll or load as necessary
    </script>
    <script>
        document.getElementById("joinBtn").addEventListener("click", function () {
            // Redirect to the registration page
            window.location.href = "/Register";
        });

    </script>

</body>

</html>